    "The self-attention mechanism is an important part of the transformer, and its unique design allows it to handle variablelength inputs, capture long-distance dependencies, and seq2seq.where q, k, and v are vectors of input X after linear mapping, and d k is the dimension of the vector.",
    "After parallel computing, the multihead attention mechanism extracts features from multiple self-attention mechanism modules and concatenates them in the channel dimension.",
